<plot>Billy Wilder, an adult film director, finds himself alone after losing his sight during a bizarre incident on the set of his last movie. Blind and unable to work, Billy spends his days stumbling around the house alone. In a ploy for companionship , Billy posts an ad for a foreign maid. Billy hires Rosa, a good Catholic girl in desperate need of work to avoid eviction.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?551444</url></doc>
